          </lg>
          <lg met="upajāti" n="8">
            <l n="a"><lb n="A15"></lb><g type="circleTarget">.</g> puṇyāyu<unclear>ṣa</unclear>ḥ kṣīṇatayā yuge 'ntye <space></space></l>
